0skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20gave%20Dhoni%20a%20huge%20compliment%2C%20saying%20his%20power-hitting%20with%20just%20four%20balls%20remaining%20made%20the%20difference%20between%20victory%20and%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni%2C%2042%2C%20scored%2020%20off%20four%20deliveries%2C%20which%20in%20the%20end%20made%20the%20difference%20to%20the%20match's%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20young%20wicketkeeper%20(MSD)%20scoring%20three%20sixes%20down%20the%20order%20helped%20a%20lot%20and%20I%20think%20that%20was%20the%20difference.%20To%20start%20off%2C%20on%20this%20kind%20of%20ground%2C%20you%20need%2010-15%20extra%20runs.%20We%20were%20looking%20at%20215-220%2C%20but%20Bumrah%20bowled%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gaikwad%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20captaincy%20duties%20from%20Dhoni%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBowling-wise%2C%20we%20were%20spot-on%20with%20our%20execution.%20Even%20in%20powerplay%2C%20I%20would%20have%20taken%20six%20overs%20for%2060.%20These%20kinds%20of%20venues%20demand%20both%20skills%3A%20batting%20and%20bowling.%20Our%20(Lasith)%20Malinga%20(Matheesha%20Pathirana)%20bowled%20exceptionally%20well%20and%20nailed%20those%20yorkers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20he%20did%20not%20open%20the%20innings%20and%20instead%20sent%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20with%20Rachin%20Ravindra%2C%20Gaikwad%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNothing%2C%20Jinks%20(Rahane)%20was%20carrying%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20niggle.%20Thought%20it%20was%20better%20for%20him%20to%20open%20and%20get%20away%20quick%20runs.%20I'm%20fine%20batting%20anywhere.%26quot%3B%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%2C%20Pathirana%2C%20who%20grabbed%20his%20best%20IPL%20figures%20of%204%2F28%2C%20said%20he%20was%20a%20bit%20nervous%20as%20he%20was%20coming%20back%20into%20the%20side%20after%20recovering%20from%20a%20niggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20bowled%20in%20powerplay%2C%20I%20was%20nervous.%20I%20don't%20think%20about%20results%20and%20I%20just%20think%20about%20execution.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20I%20was%20having%20a%20niggle%20before%20two%20weeks%20and%20all%20support%20staff%20and%20players%20helped%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20main%20thing%20to%20have%20my%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%2C%20who%20has%20modelled%20his%20action%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20legendary%20Malinga.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713165540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fm409t8a8_cs_625x300_15_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Four-young-wicketkeeper-ms-dhoni-receives-sensational-praise-from-ruturaj-gaikwad-5442461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20gave%20MS%20Dhoni%20a%20huge%20compliment%2C%20saying%20his%20power-hitting%20with%20just%20four%20balls%20remaining%20made%20the%20difference%20between%20victory%20and%20defeat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Planned%20In%20US%2C%20Executed%20In%20Mumbai%3A%20Salman%20Khan%20Firing%20Case%20Decoded%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20plan%20hatched%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20a%20network%20of%20professional%20shooters%20and%20weapon%20caches%20stockpiled%20across%20multiple%20Indian%20states%20-%20the%20makings%20of%20the%20shooting%20incident%20outside%20Bollywood%20actor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsalman-khan-firing-case-man-who-fired-at-salman-khans-home-from-gurugram-wanted-for-murder-cops-5444011%5C%22%3ESalman%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E's%20residence%20resembles%20a%20crime-thriller%20script.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20at%20around%205%20am%2C%20two%20men%20on%20a%20motorcycle%20fired%20four%20rounds%20outside%20Galaxy%20Apartments%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%2C%20where%20the%20actor%20resides%2C%20and%20fled%20from%20the%20spot.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcops-release-pictures-of-suspects-in-salman-khan-home-firing-case-5440897%5C%22%3ECCTV%20installed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20area%20caught%20the%20individuals%20sporting%20caps%20and%20carrying%20backpacks.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20footage%20showed%20them%20firing%20towards%20the%20actor's%20residence.%20One%20of%20the%20suspects%20donned%20a%20white%20t-shirt%20paired%20with%20a%20black%20jacket%20and%20denim%20pants%2C%20while%20the%20other%20was%20attired%20in%20a%20red%20t-shirt%20with%20denim%20pants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20men%2C%20according%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20are%20part%20of%20the%20notorious%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang.%20Bishnoi%20is%20currently%20in%20Tihar%20Jail%20for%20his%20involvement%20in%20several%20high-profile%20murder%20cases%20including%20that%20of%20musician%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20and%20Rajput%20leader%20and%20Karni%20Sena%20chief%20Sukhdev%20Singh%20Gogamedi%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Plot%20Was%20Hatched%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20originated%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20where%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%2C%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi's%20brother%2C%20entrusted%20the%20task%20of%20selecting%20shooters%20to%20Rohit%20Godara%2C%20another%20gangster%20also%20based%20in%20the%20US.%20This%20decision%20was%20likely%20influenced%20by%20Godara's%20extensive%20network%20of%20professional%20shooters%20spanning%20several%20states%20in%20India%2C%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnmol%20Bishnoi%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20incident%20through%20a%20Facebook%20post.%20However%2C%20the%20IP%20address%20of%20the%20Facebook%20page%20that%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20firing%20incident%20was%20traced%20back%20to%20Canada.%20The%20police%20are%20investigating%20the%20possibility%20that%20a%20VPN%20was%20utilized%20to%20create%20the%20Facebook%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodara%20holds%20a%20key%20position%20in%20the%20Bishnoi%20gang%20due%20to%20his%20involvement%20in%20previous%20high-profile%20cases%2C%20including%20the%20Raju%20Theth%20murder%20case%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20the%20Gogamedi%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bishnoi%20gang%20maintains%20a%20ready%20supply%20of%20weapons%20strategically%20stored%20in%20various%20locations%20across%20multiple%20states%2C%20police%20said.%20It%20is%20suspected%20that%20Godara%20facilitated%20the%20provision%20of%20weapons%20to%20the%20shooters%20through%20his%20associates%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishal%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Kalu%2C%20emerged%20as%20a%20prime%20candidate%20for%20the%20job%20due%20to%20his%20involvement%20in%20previous%20violent%20incidents%20orchestrated%20by%20Godara.%20Vishal%20is%20wanted%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20March%20murder%20of%20Gurugram-based%20businessman%20Sachin%20Munjal.%20Godara%20reportedly%20confessed%20to%20Munjal's%20killing%20via%20a%20social%20media%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishal%20and%20the%20other%20suspect%20purchased%20a%20second-hand%20bike%20from%20Raigad%20district%20to%20reach%20Mr%20Khan's%20residence.%20They%20travelled%20to%20Mumbai%20on%20that%20bike%20from%20Panvel.%20The%20police%20are%20questioning%20individuals%20about%20the%20sale%20of%20this%20bike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20said%20that%20the%20police%20vehicle%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20stationed%20outside%20Mr%20Khan's%20house%2C%20was%20not%20present%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20from%20five%20states%20-%20Maharashtra%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Punjab%20-%20have%20initiated%20a%20coordinated%20effort%20to%20apprehend%20those%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrevious%20Threats%20To%20Salman%20Khan%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20said%20that%20Mr%20Khan%20topped%20the%20list%20of%2010%20main%20targets%20that%20jailed%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20planned%20to%20eliminate%2C%20citing%20the%20actor's%20infamous%201998%20black%20buck%20hunting%20incident%2C%20which%20according%20to%20the%20gangster%2C%20offended%20the%20Bishnoi%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Police%20escalated%20Mr%20Khan's%20security%20status%20to%20Y%2B%2C%20following%20another%20threat%20call%20made%20on%20April%2011%20last%20year.%20Currently%2C%20the%20Y%2B%20security%20is%20undergoing%20review.%20Eleven%20security%20personnel%20accompany%20Mr%20Khan%20at%20all%20times%2C%20including%20one%20or%20two%20commandos%20and%20two%20%C2%A0Personal%20Security%20Officers%20(PSO).%20Two%20vehicles%20always%20accompany%20Mr%20Khan's%20car%2C%20one%20in%20front%20and%20one%20behind%20and%20the%20car%20is%20fully%20bulletproof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lookout%20circular%20(LOC)%20was%20issued%20against%20an%20Indian%20student%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20for%20allegedly%20sending%20a%20threatening%20email%20to%20Mr%20Khan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20of%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20both%20the%20Maharashtra%20ATS%20and%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20have%20also%20requested%20detailed%20information%20about%20the%20case.%20While%20the%20case%20was%20transferred%20from%20the%20local%20police%20to%20the%20crime%20branch%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20communication%20or%20request%20to%20transfer%20the%20case%20to%20the%20ATS%20or%20NIA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713165480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fr64jt9lg_salman-khan-firing-case-_625x300_15_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fplanned-in-us-executed-in-mumbai-salman-khan-firing-case-decoded-5444575%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Salman%20Khan%20firing%20case%3A%20A%20plan%20hatched%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20a%20network%20of%20professional%20shooters%20and%20weapon%20caches%20stockpiled%20across%20multiple%20Indian%20states%20-%20the%20makings%20of%20the%20shooting%20incident%20outside%20