8%25%2C%20have%20switched%20sides%20to%20join%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Findia-decides%2Fwhat-s-behind-congress-s-endless-exodus-fickle-loyalties-or-fading-fortunes-773877%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20highest%20number%20of%20such%20defectors%2C%2037%2C%20are%20from%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Indian%20politics%2C%20the%20phrase%20'%3Cem%3EAya%20Ram%20Gaya%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E'%20is%20often%20used%20to%20describe%20politicians%20who%20frequently%20switch%20parties.%20The%20story%20goes%20that%20Gaya%20Lal%2C%20an%20MLA%20from%20Hodal%2C%20Haryana%2C%20won%20the%20election%20as%20an%20independent%20candidate%20in%201967%20and%20joined%20the%20Congress.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20changed%20parties%20thrice%20in%2015%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%201967%20and%201983%2C%20there%20were%20approximately%202%2C700%20defections%20at%20the%20state%20level.%20As%20many%20as%2015%20defectors%20went%20on%20to%20become%20chief%20ministers.%20This%20high%20number%20of%20defections%20led%20to%20the%20enactment%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhimachal-pradesh-rajya-sabha-polls-anti-defection-law-doesnt-apply-6-rebel-congress-mlas-to-himachal-speaker-5144299%5C%22%3EAnti-Defection%20Law%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2052nd%20Amendment%20Act%20of%201985.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20anti-defection%20law%20is%20in%20place%2C%20it%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20circumvent%20it.%20The%20Supreme%20Court's%20rulings%20on%20this%20matter%20have%20also%20not%20been%20enough%20to%20curb%20the%20malaise.%20Politicians%20now%20often%20resign%20from%20their%20original%20party%2C%20instead%20of%20formally%20'crossing%20the%20floor'%20or%20voting%20against%20their%20party%20in%20a%20confidence%20motion.%20This%20sidesteps%20the%20law%2C%20while%20bringing%20down%20the%20party's%20strength%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20of%20433%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20who%20changed%20parties%20and%20re-contested%20elections%20held%20between%202016%20and%202020%20shows%20that%20out%20of%20405%20MLAs%20who%20switched%20political%20parties%2C%20182%2C%20almost%2045%25%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20Out%20of%2016%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20who%20switched%20political%20parties%2C%2010%2C%20that%20is%20over%2060%25%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20instances%20from%20recent%20history%20where%20democratically%20elected%20state%20governments%20have%20been%20toppled%20through%20defections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Karnataka%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20party%20or%20coalition%20needs%20113%20seats%20for%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20224-member%20state%20assembly.%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20(JD-S)%20formed%20a%20coalition%20government%20in%202018%20with%20115%20MLAs.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-bs-yediyurappa-takes-oath-as-karnataka-chief-minister-for-fourth-time-2075966%5C%22%3E13%20MLAs%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20three%20MLAs%20of%20the%20JD(S)%3C%2Fa%3E%20resigned%20within%2014%20months%2C%20reducing%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20House%20to%20208%2C%20and%20the%20majority%20mark%20came%20down%20to%20105%20seats.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20exactly%20105%20MLAs%2C%20proved%20its%20majority%20and%20formed%20the%20next%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fall%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-by-elections-gaddari-is-word-of-the-week-as-kamal-nath-duels-bjp-2317199%5C%22%3EKamal%20Nath-led%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20with%20the%20resignation%20of%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20from%20his%20seat%20in%20Parliament.%20Following%20this%2C%20MLAs%20loyal%20to%20Scindia%2C%20including%20six%20ministers%2C%20resigned.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20toppling%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20and%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan-led%20BJP%20government.%20Scindia%20was%20awarded%20by%20being%20made%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Union%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Manipur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202017%20Manipur%20Assembly%20Elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%2028%20seats%20and%20the%20BJP%2021.%20The%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%2060-member%20House%20is%2031.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20together%20had%2030%20seats.%20The%20BJP%20got%20a%20single%20Congress%20MLA%20to%20form%20the%20government.%20Later%2C%20eight%20other%20Congress%20MLAs%20lent%20their%20'unofficial'%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20Congress%20MLAs%20who%20supported%20the%20BJP%20never%20actually%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%20or%20issued%20letters%20of%20support%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20government.%20They%20even%20continued%20sitting%20in%20the%20Opposition%20benches%20to%20avoid%20violating%20the%20anti-defection%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20forming%20the%20government%20in%202014%2C%20Congress%20Chief%20Minister%20Pema%20Khandu%20took%2043%20of%20his%20party%20MLAs%20with%20him%20in%202016%20and%20joined%20the%20People's%20Party%20of%20Arunachal%20(PPA)%2C%20which%20was%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20that%20year%2C%2033%20PPA%20MLAs%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20formed%20the%20government.%20Later%2C%20two%20more%20Congress%20MLAs%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Within%20a%20span%20of%20one%20year%2C%20mass%20defections%20brought%20the%20number%20of%20Congress%20MLAs%20down%20from%2047%20to%20just%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20105%20seats%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20with%2056%2C%20the%20NCP%2054%20and%20the%20Congress%2044.%20The%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%20288-member%20House%20is%20145.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20were%20to%20form%20the%20government%3B%20however%2C%20they%20had%20a%20falling%20out.%20When%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20non-BJP%20government%20was%20imminent%2C%20President's%20Rule%20was%20imposed%20in%20the%20state.%20On%20November%2023%2C%202019%2C%20at%205.47%20a.m.%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20invoked%20Rule%2012%20of%20the%20Transaction%20of%20Business%20Rules%2C%201961%2C%20which%20empowered%20it%20to%20revoke%20the%20proclamation%20of%20President's%20Rule%20in%20Maharashtra%20without%20the%20prior%20approval%20of%20the%20Union%20Cabinet.%20This%20allowed%20the%20BJP%20a%20chance%20to%20form%20the%20government%20when%20it%20briefly%20gained%20the%20support%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resultant%20government%20lasted%20just%2080%20hours.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20Fadnavis%20resigned.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20coalition%20government%20comprising%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20and%20the%20Congress.%20In%20June%202022%2C%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20member%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20with%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20MLAs%2C%20revoked%20support%20to%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20and%20claimed%20to%20be%20the%20real%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Shinde%20and%20his%20MLAs%20then%20formed%20a%20government%20in%20coalition%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20former%20chief%20minister%20Fadnavis%20as%20his%20deputy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20incidents%20highlight%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20reassess%20the%20existing%20anti-defection%20law%20and%20give%20it%20more%20teeth.%20Blatant%20subversion%20of%20people's%20mandates%20must%20come%20to%20a%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713160800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-09%2Fbjp-logo-flag-generic_650x400_61443290859.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-fluid-friendships-over-a-quarter-of-bjp-candidates-are-defectors-5444751%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20to%20reassess%20the%20existing%20anti-defection%20law%20and%20give%20it%20more%20teeth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-fluid-friendships-over-a-quarter-of-bjp-candidates-are-defectors-5444751%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer%20%26amp%3B%20Kriti%20grace%20the%20Varanasi%20ramp%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713160607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109303728%2Cimgsize-52112.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-and-kriti-sanon-grace-the-varanasi-ramp-event%2Farticleshow%2F109303756.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109303756.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanveer%20and%20Kriti%20graced%20the%20ramp%20in%20Varanasi%20for%20a%20fashion%20show%20celebrating%20Banarasi%20Saree%20and%20the%20weaver%20community.%20The%20event%2C%20organized%20by%20Manish%20Malhotra%2C%20showcased%20exquisite%20craftsmanship%20and%20received%20praise%20from%20both%20actors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-and-kriti-sanon-grace-the-varanasi-ramp-event%2Farticleshow%2F109303756.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmp