09302500.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Weeks%20Left%20For%20Polls%20In%20Delhi%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Supreme%20Court%20Date%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20less%20than%20seven%20weeks%20to%20go%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-gave-orders-to-atishi-from-jail-through-lawyers-delhi-court-5414224%5C%22%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E's%20petition%20against%20his%20arrest%20by%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20will%20come%20up%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2021%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20denied%20relief%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20on%20Tuesday.%20Rejecting%20his%20petition%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said%20the%20central%20probe%20agency%20had%20submitted%20material%20to%20suggest%20that%20he%20had%20allegedly%20conspired%20to%20formulate%20the%20policy%20and%20was%20involved%20in%20demanding%20claimed%20kickbacks%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20the%20verdict%2C%20the%20AAP%20leader%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20relief.%20However%2C%20he%20could%20not%20get%20an%20urgent%20hearing.%20Then%2C%20the%20court%20was%20closed%20for%20Eid%20and%20the%20weekend.%20Today%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20will%20hear%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20petition%20around%2010.30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20appeal%20against%20the%20high%20court%20ruling%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20his%20arrest%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20was%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%20by%20extraneous%20considerations%26quot%3B.%20The%20appeal%20says%20that%20a%20sitting%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bmotivated%20manner%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20election%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20that%20his%20arrest%20constitutes%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20assault%20on%20the%20tenets%20of%20democracy%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bfree%20and%20fair%20elections%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfederalism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20after%20he%20skipped%20multiple%20summonses%2C%20is%20the%20third%20senior%20AAP%20leader%20to%20be%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%20Earlier%2C%20his%20former%20deputy%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%20Mr%20Singh%20is%20now%20out%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED's%20money%20laundering%20investigation%20in%20based%20on%20a%202022%20CBI%20case%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20excise%20policy.%20The%20CBI%20case%20registered%20the%20case%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20hatched%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%20while%20preparing%20the%20liquor%20policy%20and%20deliberately%20left%20loopholes%20to%20favour%20some%20licensees.%20The%20liquor%20policy%20was%20withdrawn%20nine%20months%20after%20its%20implementation%20amid%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20and%20a%20political%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20against%20its%20leaders%20and%20stressed%20that%20ED%20officials%20did%20not%20find%20a%20penny%20during%20its%20raids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20talking%20about%20crores.%20But%20ED%20and%20CBI%20have%20not%20found%20even%20a%20rupee%20of%20illegal%20money.%20Witnesses%20have%20been%20pressured%20to%20change%20their%20statements%20and%20say%20what%20ED%20wants%20them%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Delhi%20minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20has%20said