0the%20resignation%20of%20the%20Kejriwal%20government%20in%202014.%20A%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leader%20was%20caught%20on%20camera%20offering%20Rs%204%20crore%20to%20an%20AAP%20MLA%20then.%20In%20Kejariwal's%20second%20stint%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fin-fresh-aap-crisis-arvind-kejriwal-sacks-water-minister-kapil-mishra-1690410%5C%22%3EKapil%20Mishra%2C%20a%20minister%20was%20sacked%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20serious%20attempt%20was%20made%20to%20lure%20a%20large%20section%20of%20MLAs%20to%20dislodge%20the%20government.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20a%20timely%20intervention%2C%20those%20attempts%20did%20not%20work.%20But%20the%20AAP%20is%20extremely%20vulnerable%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20AAP%20is%20operating%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20Kejriwal%20is%20not%20available%2024%2F7.%20Though%20he%20has%20not%20resigned%20as%20CM%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20national%20convener%20of%20the%20party%2C%20his%20manoeuvring%20capacity%20is%20extremely%20limited.%20The%20party%20is%20basically%20trying%20to%20swim%20without%20his%20'life%20guard'%20services.%20And%20this%20is%20happening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20AAP's%20inception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeft%20Rudderless%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20is%20heavily%20centralised%20around%20Kejriwal.%20No%20member%2C%20office-bearer%2C%20MLA%2C%20MP%20or%20minister%20is%20free%20to%20take%20decisions%20without%20consulting%20the%20top%20boss.%20There%20is%20no%20party%20structure.%20The%20functioning%20of%20the%20AAP%20so%20far%20can%20best%20be%20described%20as%20a%20'programmed%20robot'%20that%20will%20act%20or%20do%20as%20per%20the%20programmed%20software.%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20has%20crippled%20AAP.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20party%20has%20shown%20remarkable%20capacity%20to%20fight%20back.%20One%20of%20the%20reasons%20is%20that%20Kejriwal%20anticipated%20much%20in%20advance%20that%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20he%20would%20be%20arrested%2C%20and%20accordingly%20prepared%20a%20blueprint%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20crisis.%20He%20had%20also%20delegated%20responsibilities%20to%20leaders%20who%20would%20deal%20with%20the%20situation%20in%20his%20absence.%20And%20he%20continues%20to%20give%20instructions%20from%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saving%20grace%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-mp-sanjay-singh-released-from-tihar-jail-after-6-months-5368051%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Singh%20is%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20bail%20after%20spending%20six%20months%20in%20jail.%20He%20is%20third%20in%20the%20party's%20pecking%20order%20after%20Kejriwal%20and%20Manish%20Sisodia.%20A%20street%20fighter%2C%20he%20is%20highly%20political%20and%20has%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20party%20cadre%20and%20leaders.%20His%20release%20has%20certainly%20given%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20life%20to%20the%20beleaguered%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstitutional%20Morality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kejriwal's%20insistence%20that%20he%20will%20run%20the%20government%20from%20jail%20can%20prove%20to%20be%20the%20undoing%20of%20not%20only%20the%20government%20but%20also%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Ideally%2C%20before%20going%20to%20jail%2C%20he%20should%20have%20handed%20over%20the%20baton%20to%20his%20most%20trusted%20aide.%20Unlike%20Lalu%20Yadav%2C%20Jayalalithaa%20and%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20he%20did%20not%20choose%20his%20successor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal's%20action%20might%20not%2C%20technically%2C%20violate%20the%20Constitution%20as%20it%20is%20silent%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20a%20chief%20minister%20can%20run%20the%20government%20from%20jail.%20But%20his%20action%20does%20not%20follow%20constitutional%20morality%20and%20disrespects%20basic%20ethos.%20Kejriwal%20is%20known%20to%20defy%20the%20established%20path%2C%20and%20that%20is%20also%20the%20reason%20for%20his%20spectacular%20success.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20he%20seems%20to%20have%20erred%20in%20his%20judgment%2C%20and%20that%20might%20cost%20him%20and%20the%20party%20dearly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20rejected%20three%20petitions%20seeking%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20continuing%20to%20be%20chief%20minister.%20The%20court%20has%20also%20declined%20to%20entertain%20the%20request.%20Asserting%20that%20a%20remedy%20is%20available%20within%20the%20executive%20branch%2C%20it%20refrained%20from%20overstepping%20into%20others'%20jurisdiction.%20Sooner%20or%20later%2C%20the%20central%20government%20will%20have%20to%20take%20a%20decision.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20for%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20Kejriwal%2C%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20is%20'incapacitated'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Routes%20To%20Take%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20leader%20assumes%20office%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%2Fshe%20is%20expected%20to%20fulfil%20duties%20accordingly.%20If%20the%20individual%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20so%2C%20the%20continuation%20in%20office%20should%20be%20scrutinised.%20In%20such%20exceptional%20circumstances%2C%20two%20institutions%20can%20intervene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20option%20is%20that%20the%20party%20can%20convene%20a%20meeting%20of%20its%20legislature%20to%20select%20a%20new%20leader.%20The%20Lieutenant-Governor%20or%20the%20Governor%2C%20as%20applicable%2C%20should%20be%20informed%2C%20and%20the%20new%20cabinet%20should%20be%20installed%2C%20replacing%20the%20incumbent.%20In%20the%20current%20case%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20the%20AAP%20will%20do%20something%20like%20that.%20The%20whole%20party%20is%20solidly%20behind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20scenario%2C%20the%20L-G%20of%20Delhi%20can%20take%20the%20initiative.%20He%20can%20do%20two%20things.%20First%2C%20he%20can%20send%20a%20report%20to%20the%20central%20government%20that%20there%20is%20a%20breakdown%20of%20constitutional%20machinery%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20President's%20rule%20should%20be%20imposed.%20I%20am%20against%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20President's%20rule%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country%20if%20there%20is%20a%20duly%20elected%20government.%20But%20Delhi%20is%20an%20exception.%20In%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20there%20%3Cem%3Eis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20duly%20elected%20government%2C%20but%20neither%20the%20chief%20minister%20nor%20his%20party%20has%20shown%20an%20inclination%20to%20adhere%20to%20constitutional%20morality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20L-G%20can%20send%20a%20message%20to%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20through%20the%20speaker%2C%20advising%20that%20since%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20is%20incapacitated%20and%20can't%20discharge%20his%20duties%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20house%20is%20duty-bound%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20leader%3B%20and%2C%20if%20the%20house%20chooses%20to%20ignore%20his%20advice%2C%20he%20can%20ask%20the%20central%20government%20to%20impose%20President's%20rule.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoing%20Against%20Tradition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20mistake%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20only%20a%20written%20document.%20It%20is%20a%20living%20organism%20and%20evolves%20with%20traditions%20and%20conventions.%20As%20per%20constitutional%20tradition%2C%20a%20chief%20minister%2C%20once%20accused%20of%20corruption%20charges%2C%20resigns%20if%20jail%20becomes%20imminent.%20If%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20party%20do%20not%20want%20to%20follow%20the%20constitutional%20tradition%2C%20the%20L-G%20can't%20wait%20for%20eternity%20for%20him%20to%20resign.%20If%20he%20does%20that%2C%20then%20it%20means%20both%20the%20functionaries%20-%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20L-G%20-%C2%A0%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20not%20following%20the%20constitutional%20morality%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20central%20government%20will%20have%20to%20step%20in%20sooner%20than%20later.%20The%20world%20is%20watching.%20It%20may%20like%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-moves-supreme-court-against-his-arrest-in-liquor-policy-case-after-high-court-setback-5410271%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court's%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20the%20case%20today.%20Either%20way%2C%20the%20AAP%20government%20is%20staring%20at%20a%20big%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20co-founder%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.satyahindi.com%2F%5C%22%3ESatyaHindi.com%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713149220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhb1ndiok_arvind-kejriwal-pti_625x300_12_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-it-the-beginning-of-the-end-for-aap-government-in-delhi-5443910%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AAP%20is%20heavily%20centralised%20around%20Kejriwal.%20The%20party%20is%20basically%20trying%20to%20swim%20without%20his%20'life%20guard'%20services.%20And%20this%20is%20happening%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20AAP's%20inception.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fis-it-the-beginning-of-the-end-for-aap-government-in-delhi-5443910%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20Loses%20Top%20Phonemaker%20Spot%20To%20Samsung%20As%20iPhone%20Shipments%20Drop%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple's%20smartphone%20shipments%20dropped%20about%2010%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20hurt%20by%20intensifying%20competition%20by%20Android%20sm