versity%20marketing%20professor%20and%20successful%20entrepreneur%20recently%20emphasised%20storytelling%20as%20a%20key%20skill%20for%20young%20people%20entering%20the%20workforce.%20Scott%20Galloway%2C%20a%20millionaire%20who%20sold%20his%20company%20for%20over%20%24130%20million%2C%20believes%20effective%20communication%20is%20crucial%20in%20a%20world%20increasingly%20reliant%20on%20technology.%20While%20platforms%20may%20evolve%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20articulate%20ideas%20with%20data%20and%20visuals%20is%20timeless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20give%20my%2013%20and%2016-year-old%20one%20competence%20that%20I%20think%20would%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20time%2C%20it'd%20be%20storytelling%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2059-year-old%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F04%2F08%2Fscott-galloway-this-is-the-no-1-skill-young-people-need-it-isnt-ai.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNBC%20Make%20It%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mr%20Galloway%20added%20that%20the%20type%20of%20storytelling%20may%20not%20matter%20because%20the%20platforms%20people%20use%20to%20communicate%20can%20change%20rapidly.%20Still%2C%20the%20important%20part%20is%20developing%20an%20%26quot%3Bability%20to%20write%20well%2C%20an%20ability%20to%20articulate%20ideas%20and%20an%20ability%20to%20present%20ideas%20with%20data%2C%20infographics%2C%20slideshows%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Galloway%20in%20an%20interaction%20with%20CNBC%20Make%20It%20warns%20against%20solely%20relying%20on%20AI%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT.%20The%20future%20of%20AI%20and%20coding%20is%20uncertain%2C%20and%20strong%20storytelling%20will%20always%20be%20a%20valuable%20asset.%20He%20also%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20expertise%20-%20becoming%20an%20authority%20in%20your%20field%20is%20a%20reliable%20path%20to%20success%2C%20regardless%20of%20technological%20advancements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Galloway%20told%20the%20media%20outlet%20how%20a%20brand's%20storytelling%20can%20directly%20contribute%20to%2C%20or%20hurt%2C%20its%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20importance%20of%20storytelling%20is%20particularly%20why%20young%20people%20shouldn't%20rely%20solely%20on%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence%20tools%20like%20ChatGPT%20-%20not%20now%2C%20not%20ever%2C%20said%20Galloway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20if%20in%20five%20years%20some%20neural%20network%20is%20going%20to%20replace%20ChatGPT.%20We%20don't%20know%20if%20coding%20is%20going%20to%20be%20outdated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20specific%20crowds%20out%20the%20general%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Galloway%20added.%20%26quot%3BFind%20a%20niche%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20narrow%20it%20is%2C%20and%20try%20and%20own%20it.%20Commit%20to%20being%20one%20of%20the%20most%20knowledgeable%20people%20in%20the%20world%20on%20a%20domain...%20You're%20never%20going%20to%20be%20an%20expert%20in%20anything%20if%20you%20don't%20enjoy%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713148320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F76rbo5ag_scott-galloway_625x300_15_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmillionaire-entrepreneur-reveals-no-1-skill-for-the-ai-era-its-not-coding-5443907%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scott%20Galloway%2C%20a%20millionaire%2C%20believes%20effective%20communication%20is%20crucial%20in%20a%20world%20increasingly%20reliant%20on%20technology%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmillionaire-entrepreneur-reveals-no-1-skill-for-the-ai-era-its-not-coding-5443907%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmillionaire-entrepreneur-reveals-no-1-skill-for-the-ai-era-its-not-coding-5443907%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmillionaire-entrepreneur-reveals-no-1-skill-for