%3Ch2%3E'Who%20dares%20disturb%20my%20slumber%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20animated%20character%20Vincent%20Valentine.%20Voice%20actor%20Matthew%20Mercer%20(right)%20voices%20the%20character%20in%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%20VII%3A%20Rebirth.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618a26616bde8d4ead82ef4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMatt%20Mercer%2C%20of%20%26quot%3BCritical%20Role%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Legend%20of%20Zelda%3A%20Tears%20of%20the%20Kingdom%26quot%3B%20fame%2C%20voices%20Vincent%20Valentine.%3Cp%3ESquare%20Enix%3B%20Gregg%20DeGuire%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMercer's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC1h3ufMcS2Y%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopening%20line%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%20VII%3A%20Rebirth%26quot%3B%20is%20now%20a%20fandom%20legend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20deep%20growl%20of%20%26quot%3BWho%20dares%20disturb%20my%20slumber%3F%26quot%3B%20from%20within%20the%20depths%20of%20his%20velvet-lined%20coffin%2C%20longtime%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%26quot%3B%20fans%20were%20introduced%20to%20the%20super-cool%2C%20uber-goth%20gunslinger.%20(Spoiler%20alert%3A%20Valentine%20looks%20like%20a%20vampire.%20But%20he's%20not%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20one%20in%20the%20strictest%20definition%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%94%20he%20just%20has%20multiple%20monstrous%20forms%2C%20and%20takes%20long%20rests%20in%20a%20casket.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVincent%20is%20like%20the%20dark%20edge%20lord%20of%20emo%20sadness%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20and%20then%20has%20this%20kind%20of%20burning%20fire%20of%20passion%20on%20the%20inside%20that%20begins%20to%20kindle%20as%20his%20story%20revs%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20had%20a%20thought%20in%20my%20head%20of%20how%20he%20would%20sound.%20And%20now%20I%20just%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20let%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ask%20him%20about%20the%20fandom's%20love%20for%20vampire-like%20characters%2C%20and%20he%20agrees%20they%20are%20%3Cem%3Eso%3C%2Fem%3E%20back%20in%20the%20limelight.%20Mercer%20also%20voices%20a%20vampire%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Legend%20of%20Vox%20Machina%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Amazon-backed%20animated%20series%20he%20created%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcritical-role-dungeons-dragons-sold-out-live-show-wembley-arena-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20friends%20at%20Critical%20Role.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVincent%20definitely%20embodies%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20classic%20fantasy%2C%20media-informed%20kind%20of%20antihero%20protagonist%20vampires%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20he%20thinks%20the%20essence%20of%20a%20vampire's%20allure%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20tragedy%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bsteeped%20in%20its%20own%20mythology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20person%20who%20is%20plucked%20from%20the%20cycle%20of%20life%2C%20and%20to%20subsist%20and%20exist%20is%20to%20feast%20on%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20very%20vibe%20itself%20is%20tragic%20and%20romantic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVincent%20very%20much%20borrows%20that%20aesthetic%20of%20'the%20monster%20within%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20'I%20try%20to%20be%20as%20good%20as%20I%20can%2C%20but%20there's%20something%20dark%20inside%20me%20that%20I'm%20ever%20having%20to%20keep%20at%20bay.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20%26quot%3Bwild%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20says%2C%20to%20be%20immortalized%20in%20a%20game%20like%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%20VII.%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20me%20he%20grew%20up%20with%20the%20series%2C%20played%20early%20versions%20of%20the%20game%2C%20and%20cosplayed%20characters%20from%20it%2C%20so%20clinching%20this%20role%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20whale%26quot%3B%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVincent's%20kind%20of%20emerging%20from%20his%20cave%2C%20shaking%20off%20the%20dust%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20learning%20how%20to%20be%20social%2C%20and%20coming%20out%20of%20his%20shell%20of%20self-loathing%2C%26quot%3B%20Mercer%20said.%20%26quot%3BPlaying%20that%20subtle%20arc%20and%20the%20slow%20opening%20of%20that%20cold%20exterior%20has%20been%20a%20fun%20journey%20to%20explore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EVideo%20games'%20vampire%20boyfriends%20are%20also%20a%20lesson%20in%20vulnerability%20%E2%80%94%20and%20navigating%20trauma%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20actor%20Neil%20Newbon%20and%20his%20character%20from%20%26quot%3BBaldur's%20Gate%203%2C%26quot%3B%20Astarion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618a1cd1caec1275a6f6429%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20BAFTA-nominated%20Neil%20Newbon%20is%20the%20voice%20of%20Astarion.%3Cp%3EScott%20Garfitt%2FBAFTA%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Larian%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20caught%20up%20with%20Newbon%2C%20who's%20won%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fastarion-voice-actor-neil-newbon-win-best-performance-game-awards-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20accolades%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20role%20as%20Astarion%20%E2%80%94%20a%20beautiful%2C%20200-something-year-old%20vampire%20who's%20captured%20the%20hearts%20of%20many%20a%20%26quot%3BBaldur's%20Gate%203%26quot%3B%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20tough%20to%20navigate%20the%20pain%20written%20into%20Astarion's%20harrowing%20vampire-origin%20story%2C%20Newbon%20told%20me.%20Because%20there%20are%20several%20ways%20Astarion's%20character%20arc%20can%20play%20out%20based%20on%20player%20choices%2C%20Newbon%20says%20those%20who%20befriend%20the%20vampire%20in-game%20get%20to%20see%20him%20%26quot%3Bshake%20off%20a%20cloak%20of%20caution%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20be%20vulnerable%20and%20genuine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he's%20heard%20that%20people%20relate%20to%20Astarion%20because%20of%20how%20the%20character%20survives%20the%20trauma%20of%20his%20past%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20player%20gets%20to%20help%20him%20through%20it%20all%20and%20see%20his%20tragic%20tale%20to%20its%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20it%20has%20meant%20that%20they've%20been%20seen%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20feel%20alone%20in%20their%20personal%20experiences%2C%20some%20of%20which%20can%20be%20horrific%2C%20difficult%2C%20and%20leave%20a%20scar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20important%20aspect%20of%20the%20character%20that%20likely%20appeals%20to%20people%2C%20Newbon%20said%2C%20is%20his%20pursuit%20of%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAstarion's%20prime%20objective%20is%20to%20be%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20the%20idea%20that%20people%20can%20be%20free%20to%20choose%20to%20love%20who%20they%20want%20and%20how%20to%20live%20their%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%2C%20like%20many%20fans%2C%20loves%20Astarion%20deeply%20now%20%E2%80%94%20and%20would%20play%20him%20again%20in%20a%20heartbeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20viewers%20of%20the%20work%20see%2C%20too%2C%20that%20there's%20more%20underneath%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20person%20than%20the%20trope%20of%20this%20decadent%2C%20hedonistic%2C%20theatrical%20vampire%2C%26quot%3B%20Newbon%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20soul%20worth%20saving%20under%20there%2C%20so%20don't%20judge%20a%20book%20by%20its%20cover.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvampire-boyfriend-is-cool-again-astorian-vincent-valentine-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C