%26quot%3B%20with%20family%20and%20friends.%20In%20contrast%2C%20people%20generally%20go%20to%20limited-service%20restaurants%20for%20the%20speed%20and%20convenience%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWages%20could%20soar%20across%20the%20entire%20restaurant%20industry%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20say%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20predict%20exactly%20how%20diners'%20habits%20will%20change%20in%20response%20to%20the%20price%20increases%20at%20fast-food%20chains.%20People%20could%20buy%20more%20groceries%2C%20choose%20fast-food%20value%20deals%2C%20or%20switch%20to%20different%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20analysts%20do%20expect%20other%20employers%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%94%20like%20full-service%20restaurants%20and%20retailers%20%E2%80%94%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-20-fast-food-wage-increase-pay-restaurants-retail-jobs-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20paying%20workers%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20that%20they%20can%20stay%20competitive%2C%20which%20could%20ultimately%20mean%20other%20restaurants%20increase%20their%20menu%20prices%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESal%20Vitalie%2C%20who%20owns%20The%20Garden%20Club%2C%20a%20restaurant%20in%20South%20San%20Francisco%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20will%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fast-food-20-minimum-wage-restaurant-raise-pay-compete-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20to%20raise%20his%20wages%20to%20compete%20with%20local%20fast-food%20chains%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20Vaccaro%20noted%20that%20servers%20at%20mid-priced%2C%20full-service%20restaurant%20chains%20are%20likely%20to%20already%20make%20%2430%20or%20more%20an%20hour%2C%20including%20tips%2C%20so%20price%20hikes%20may%20just%20be%20a%20way%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20casual%20dining%20can%20hold%20prices%20and%20doesn't%20s