%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20credit%3A%20Raison%20D%E2%80%99etre)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712904660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346785%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nestled%20beside%20the%20Beas%20River%20in%20Manali%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Raison%20D%E2%80%99etre%E2%80%99%20homestay%20by%20Shalini%20and%20Nitin%20Beri%20offers%20guests%20an%20escape%20from%20city%20life%20%E2%80%94%20featuring%20rooms%20with%20stunning%20mountain%20views%2C%20access%20to%20natural%20spring%2C%20and%20locally%20sourced%20food.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT-M%E2%80%99s%20Groundbreaking%20Innovation%20Helps%20Wheelchair%20Users%20Stand%20With%20The%20Press%20of%20a%20Button%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20mere%20touch%20of%20a%20button%2C%20a%20wheelchair%20user%20can%20now%20effortlessly%20transition%20from%20a%20sitting%20to%20a%20standing%20position%20thanks%20to%20the%20NeoStand%20%E2%80%94%20an%20indigenously%20developed%20and%20customisable%20electric%20standing%20wheelchair.%20Developed%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282128%2F5-times-cheaper-than-imports-iit-ms-kadam-helps-amputees-walk-comfortably%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETTK%20Center%20for%20Rehabilitation%20Research%20and%20Device%20Development%3C%2Fa%3E%20(R2D2)%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Madras%2C%20this%20groundbreaking%20assistive%20device%20was%20launched%20on%2020%20March%202024%2C%20at%20the%20institute%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20IIT-Madras%2C%20the%20project%20to%20develop%20NeoStand%20was%20