2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20some%20personal%20reasons%2C%20I%20had%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20publishing%20company%2C%20and%20we%20had%20a%20stock%20of%20Marathi%20language%20books%20with%20us.%20My%20mother%20and%20sister%20did%20not%20know%20much%20beyond%20farming%2C%20so%20they%20started%20a%20makeshift%20tea%20stall%20to%20meet%20our%20expenses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20phones%2C%20only%20books!%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20Bhimabai%2C%20along%20with%20her%20daughter%2C%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20what%20is%20today%20Ajjichya%20Pustakancha%20Hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20family%20moved%2C%20the%20taunts%20and%20harsh%20words%20never%20stopped%20following%20her.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20talk%20about%20how%20the%20women%20of%20the%20house%20should%20not%20wander%20around%20selling%20tea%3B%20she%20should%20take%20care%20of%20the%20house.%20But%20I%20did%20not%20care%20about%20those%20taunts%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20children%20and%20I%20slowly%20started%20to%20use%20savings%20to%20expand%20the%20tea%20stall%20and%20make%20it%20an%20eatery.%20What%20I%20noticed%20was%20that%20while%20a%20person%20would%20wait%20for%20their%20food%2C%20they%20would%20always%20be%20buried%20in%20their%20phone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20not%20converse%20with%20each%20other%20but%20would%20keep%20scrolling%20on%20their%20phone.%20I%20found%20the%20habit%20very%20absurd%20and%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20fond%20of%20reading%20but%20never%20got%20the%20chance%20to%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20reintroduce%20the%20habit%20of%20reading%20to%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBooks%20are%20our%20best%20friends.%20They%20are%20your%20companions%20in%20every%20situation.%20We%20started%20off%20with%20just%2025%20books%20in%20a%20stand%20in%20the%20eatery%20and%20it%20kept%20growing.%20We%20started%20encouraging%20people%20to%20pick%20up%20a%20book%20and%20read%20while%20we%20cook%20their%20meal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20time%20the%20food%20would%20arrive%20at%20their%20table%2C%20they%20would%20have%20already%20reached%20chapter%20two%20of%20the%20book%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-2-1710406977.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%20over%205000%20books%20at%20the%20book%20hotel%20for%20the%20consumers%20to%20read.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-2-1710406977.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-2-1710406977-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-2-1710406977-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-2-1710406977-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-2-1710406977-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344853%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20over%205%2C000%20books%20at%20the%20book%20hotel%20for%20the%20consumers%20to%20read.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20started%20to%20appreciate%20her%20initiative%20and%20word%20spread.%20The%20book%20collection%20which%20started%20with%20only%2025%20books%20has%20now%20grown%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341906%2Fwhere-to-donate-clothes-books-toys-anushka-jain-share-at-door-step-ngos-artificial-intelligence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%205%2C000%20books.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20books%20in%20the%20eatery%2C%20we%20also%20give%20free%20books%20on%20special%20occasions%20such%20as%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%20and%20Republic%20Day%20to%20initiate%20a%20habit%20of%20reading%20among%20people.%20We%20also%20have%20started%20giving%20books%20as%20gifts%20to%20hospitals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20people%20waiting%20at%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20loved%20one%20or%20for%20their%20own%20treatment%2C%20we%20hope%20our%20books%20will%20help.%20My%20mother%20believes%20that%20medicines%20treat%20your%20body%20but%20books%20heal%20your%20soul%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eatery%20has%20also%20since%20kept%20on%20growing%20and%20people%20have%20donated%20books%20to%20Aaji%E2%80%99s%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20expresses%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20delighted%20when%20I%20see%20people%20reading%20books%20at%20the%20eatery.%20All%20my%20life%2C%20I%20have%20struggled%20to%20have%20a%20stable%20life%2C%20but%20what%20kept%20me%20going%20was%20my%20children.%20For%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20always%20fond%20of%20reading%20but%20never%20got%20to%2C%20when%20I%20see%20young%20children%20come%20to%20the%20eatery%20and%20read%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20succeeded%20in%20my%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20have%20spare%20books%20that%20you%20want%20to%20donate%20to%20the%20eatery%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20Pravin%20at%209922946622%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Pravin)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712827324000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-1-1710406948.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nashik's%20Bhimabai%20Jondhale%20always%20loved%20reading%20but%20never%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20tend%20to%20her%20passion.%20Today%2C%20she%20runs%20'Ajjichya%20Pustakancha%20Hotel'%2C%20a%20unique%20book%20hotel%20which%20serves%20delicious%20meals%20along%20with%20free%20books%20to%20read!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344848%2Fnashik-bhimabai-jondhale-ajjichya-pustakancha-hotel-book-hotel-by-grandmother%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20One%20Woman%20Created%20an%20Army%20of%2075000%20Others%20to%20Fight%20Trafficking%20of%20Girls%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Pallabi%20Ghosh%20was%2012%20years%20old%2C%20she%20encountered%20her%20first%20case%20of%20a%20child%20from%20a%20nearby%20village%20being%20trafficked.%20This%20shaped%20her%20decision%20to%20dedicate%20her%20life%20to%20rescuing%20children%20who%20were%20victims%20of%20this%20horrific%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20years%2C%20Pallabi%20founded%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313315%2Fassam-pallabi-ghosh-impact-and-dialogue-foundation-rescue-children-from-trafficking%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EImpact%20and%20Dialogue%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20through%20which%20she%20has%20rescued%20over%2010%2C000%20children%2C%20who%20would%20otherwise%20fall%20prey%20to%20human%20trafficking%20and%20its%20accompanying%20evils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20she%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9COnly%20rescuing%20the%20kids%20is%20not%20enough.%20It%20is%20crucial%20to%20rehabilitate%20them%20or%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20of%20re-trafficking.%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20a%20foundation%20of%20my%20own%20that%20would%20not%20only%20rescue%20but%20also%20empower%20these%20children.%E2%80%9D%20But%20what%20will%20be%20a%20transformative%20step%2C%20shares%20Pallabi%2C%20is%20sensitising%20constables%20to%20these%20social%20evils%20as%20they%20are%20the%20first%20responders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20maintain%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20impacted%2075%2C000%20women%20if%20I%20had%20been%20insistent%20on%20podiums%20and%20properly%20executed%20events.%20I%20managed%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325386%2Fchangemakers-transform-polluted-water-bodies-idbi-bank-environment-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20huge%20impact%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20because%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20people%20personally%2C%20knocking%20one%20door%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20give%20the%20survivors%20a%20better%20life%2C%20Pallabi%20provides%20counselling%20services%2C%20upskilling%20sessions%20and%20more%20as%20she%20believes%20the%20children%20and%20women%20who%20are%20rescued%20need%20a%20brighter%20future%20to%20look%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20scope%20of%20Pallabi%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20work%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5UzKWto5Ui%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5UzKWto5Ui%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3