2summary%22%3A%22Seviyan%20or%20vermicelli%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20adaptations%20range%20from%20the%20beloved%20seviyan%20kheer%20in%20the%20North%20to%20the%20semiya%20upma%20in%20the%20South.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20explore%20the%20ingredient%E2%80%99s%20versatility%20as%20it%20found%20its%20way%20into%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20subcontinent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hearing%20Aid%20Employs%20Tech%20Used%20in%20US%20Army%20Helmets%20To%20Help%20Thousands%20Hear%3B%20Has%20Rs%205.5%20Crore%20in%20Revenues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20final%20year%20of%20studying%20robotics%2C%20electronics%2C%20and%20communication%20engineering%2C%20Kanishka%20Patel%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20news%20article%20that%20would%20shape%20his%20future.%20The%20piece%20detailed%20a%20groundbreaking%20development%20by%20the%20British%20defence%20and%20security%20firm%20BAE%20Systems%20%E2%80%94%20an%20army%20helmet%20using%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20to%20facilitate%20communication%20among%20soldiers%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%2C%20Kanishka%20delved%20into%20research%20on%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20and%20its%20potential%20applications.%20If%20it%20could%20enhance%20communication%20amidst%20the%20cacophony%20of%20warfare%2C%20he%20pondered%2C%20what%20other%20transformative%20uses%20could%20it%20serve%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMight%20it%20offer%20hope%20to%20those%20dealing%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283166%2Fuber-india-sahib-echoes-cafe-delhi-inspiring-indians%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20individuals%20with%20conditions%20like%20microtia%2C%20whose%20external%20ears%20are%20underdeveloped%3F%20Could%20this%20technology%20present%20a%20non-surgical%2C%20cost-effective%20solution%20for%20millions%20worldwide%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanishka%E2%80%99s%20mind%20buzzed%20with%20possibilities%2C%20igniting%20a%20passion%20to%20explore%20the%20untapped%20potential%20of%20this%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20resounding%20affirmation%20of%20their%20journey%2C%20Kanishka%20and%20Raj%20Shah%20have%20indeed%20forged%20a%20remarkable%20path%20over%20seven%20years.%20Through%20their%20company%20WeHear%2C%20the%20two%20have%20built%20HearNU%20%E2%80%94%20a%20hearing%20aid%20that%20uses%20bone%20conduction%20technology%2C%20offering%20a%20non-surgical%20solution%20for%20people%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss.%20They%20have%20also%20developed%20bone%20conduction%20earphones%20called%20WeHear%20OX%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20earphone%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20sit%20inside%20your%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeHear%20has%20a%20granted%20patent%20for%20its%20HearNU%20and%20is%20transforming%20the%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20young%20children%20and%20adults%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss%2C%20in%20which%20sound%20waves%20are%20not%20able%20to%20carry%20all%20the%20way%20through%20to%20the%20inner%20ear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanishka%20and%20Raj%20claim%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20only%20bone-conduction%20hearing%20aid%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Since%20their%20launch%20in%202021%2C%20they%20have%20sold%20over%2011%2C500%20devices%20and%20have%20earned%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%205.5%20crore%20in%20FY%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20in%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203%20from%20Peyush%20Bansal%2C%20valuing%20their%20company%20at%20Rs%20250%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20exactly%20is%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20and%20what%20makes%20their%20patented%20product%20unique%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMade%20in%20India%20for%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kanishka%20and%20Raj%20founded%20WeHear%20in%202021%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346836%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKanishka%20and%20Raj%20founded%20WeHear%20in%202021%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanishka%20recalls%20being%20fascinated%20by%20audio%20and%20electronics.%20He%20participated%20in%20many%20robotics%20competitions%20across%20the%20world%2C%20and%20often%20came%20across%20brilliant%20innovations%2C%20hoping%20to%20make%20one%20himself%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20about%2018%20to%2019%20pairs%20of%20earphones%20as%20I%20love%20listening%20to%20music.%20When%20I%20read%20about%20the%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20used%20in%20the%20US%20Army%2C%20I%20wondered%20about%20the%20other%20use%20cases%20for%20it.%20I%20started%20researching%20and%20developed%20a%20prototype%20of%20a%20hearing%20aid%20using%20this%20technology%20in%202017%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kanishka%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ahmedabad%20resident%20then%20spoke%20about%20this%20idea%20with%20his%20co-founder%20Raj%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20joined%20him%20to%20build%20the%20device.%20They%20were%20incubated%20at%20the%20Gujarat%20University%20Startup%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20Council%20(GUSEC)%2C%20where%20they%20received%20funding%20and%20support%20to%20start%20their%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20tweaks%2C%20when%20they%20were%20satisfied%20with%20the%20prototype%2C%20they%20partnered%20with%20the%20Bahera%20Munga%20Shala%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20a%20school%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297383%2Fmumbai-ojas-maheshwari-with-hearing-impairment-tops-iit-jee-advanced-shares-strategy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing-impaired%3C%2Fa%3E%20children%20to%20test%20their%20device.%20The%20moment%20that%20the%20duo%20dearly%20cherish%2C%20is%20the%20first%20time%20a%20child%20heard%20a%20sound%20in%20his%20life%2C%20thanks%20to%20their%20device!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20played%20some%20music%2C%20and%20the%20child%20heard%20a%20sound%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20his%20life.%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20forget%20the%20way%20his%20face%20lit%20up.%20He%20started%20enjoying%20the%20music%2C%20and%20his%20mother%20was%20in%20tears.%20That%20moment%20is%20etched%20in%20my%20memory%20forever%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2028-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20resolve%20strengthened%2C%20the%20duo%20then%20worked%20on%20perfecting%20their%20device.%20This%20journey%20was%20far%20from%20smooth%20as%20it%20took%20them%20around%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20and%20seven%20prototypes%20before%20they%20came%20up%20with%20their%20final%20device%20%E2%80%94%20the%20HearNU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20they%20felt%20that%20their%20device%20was%20ready%20for%20the%20market%20they%20did%20alpha%20and%20beta%20testing%20for%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20before%20launching%20the%20final%20version%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20device%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2uLAYuJ8wJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2uLAYuJ8wJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2uLAYuJ8wJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20WeHear%20HearNU%20(%40hearnu_official)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20device%20is%20meant%20for%20people%20who%20have%20conductive%20hearing%20loss%2C%20have%20microtia%20(a%20congenital%20ear%20deformity%20in%20which%20the%20external%20ear%20is%20malformed%20and%20underdeveloped)%2C%20or%20have%20any%20other%20problem%20in%20the%20physical%20ear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HearNU%20comes%20with%20a%20wearable%20band%2C%20which%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263747%2Fstudent-innovation-transcribe-glass-google-glass-low-cost-hearing-aid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20aid%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethrough%20Bluetooth%2C%20and%20uses%20bone%20conduction%20technology.%20The%20hearing%20aid%2C%20which%20is%20shaped%20like%20a%20band%2C%20sits%20behind%20the%20ear%20on%20the%20temporal%20bone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20device%20uses%20the%20bone%20as%20a%20conductor%20of%20sound.%20The%20device%2C%20placed%20on%20the%20temporal%20bone%2C%20sends%20vibrations%20to%20the%20cochlea.%20It%20bypasses%20the%20physical%20ear%20system%2C%20namely%20the%20outer%20ear%2C%20inner%20ear%20and%20middle%20ear%2C%20directly%20simulating%20the%20last%20part%20of%20the%20ear%2C%20which%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20brain%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Kanishk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20band%2C%20which%20the%20user%20wears%20on%20the%20hand%2C%20is%20equipped%20with%20microprocessors.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20captures%20the%20audio%20and%20sounds%2C%20tunes%20them%2C%20processes%20them%20and%20sends%20them%20to%20the%20hearing%20device%2C%20enabling%20the%20user%20to%20hear.%20The%20Bluetooth%20can%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20other%20device%20like%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20TV%2C%20or%20laptop%2C%20helping%20children%20listen%20to%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20for%20people%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss%20is%20usually%20a%20surgical%20implant%20called%20the%20BAHA%20implant%20(Bone-Anchored%20Hearing%20Aid)%2C%20which%20uses%20the%20same%20technology%20used%20in%20this%20hearing%20aid.%20The%20corresponding%20surgery%20generally%20costs%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%2C%20while%20this%20device%20costs%20Rs%2080%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20differentiator%20and%20patent%20is%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20use%20this%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20used%20in%20the%20surgery%20and%20military%20devices%2C%20for%20a%20non-surgical%20hearing%20aid%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20Of%20Speech%20and%20Hearing%20in%20Mysuru%20for%20clinical%20trials%20and%20also%20received%20grants%20from%20the%20Union%20Government%20and%20State%20Government%20worth%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20fund%20their%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20through%20this%20venture%2C%20the%20duo%20have%20provided%20the%20gift%20of%20hearing%20to%20over%2011%2C500%20children%20and%20adults%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20the%20majority%20of%20which%20are%20through%20partnerships%20with%20corporations%20and%20CSR%20activities.%20They%20also%20partner%20with%20State%20Governments%20to%20distribute%20hearing%20aids%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20HearNU%20is%20currently%20being%20exported%20to%20countries%20in%20Africa%2C%20with%20plans%20for%20global%20expansion%20supported%20by%20a%20granted%20patent%20covering%2027%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-04-at-5.19.10-PM-1712584333.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%2011%2C500%20devices%20have%20been%20sold%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-04-at-5.19.10-PM-1712584333.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.c